N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 40.8 - Advisory board

State Regulations

Advisory board means those producers who are appointed by
the commissioner pursuant to section
40.15
of this Part to advise and
assist him in administering this Part. Notes
